\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢地寧願等3-4分鐘等架𨋢都唔肯用1分鐘行樓梯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aba96aa385b7fc2eec2f9b82d651b781b9afd79","tid":223421,"uid":332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T13:41:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n住2樓日日都㩒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自認自己係on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8202971cf2ccbcda91d3f52bf8b4a056df98588a","tid":223421,"uid":89064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T14:41:35.000Z","msg":"通常果D係廢老黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6156ec4c02dfad99c55fda2420348da0b6694d96","tid":223421,"uid":67848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T17:38:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n住2樓日日都㩒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自認自己係on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你就on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己出題 自己都唔識答 有無諗過番去補下中文咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e15ab95e3d490ec9b28aa1584f4a89119557f377","tid":223421,"uid":27129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T17:41:28.000Z","msg":"我最憎等𨋢<br />\n等咁耐 不如自己行上去 仲快過搭𨋢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2eb19ebaf5c29613b6dd9580c649493512ea55b","tid":223421,"uid":50920,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T17:47:02.000Z","msg":"唐樓撚好奇一問 <br />\n住一二樓管理費會平d？"},{"pid":"81af47902b86db61094c888f3b9e20fea8fb9526","tid":223421,"uid":108756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T13:15:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唐樓撚好奇一問 <br />\n住一二樓管理費會平d？</blockquote><br />\n其實係有時啲人住比較高層數搭lift落樓個時好彩既直落地下或者停一兩層<br />\n咁有時部lift已經慢或者你都諗住差唔多到地面個時停左係3 2 1 樓隨便一層你都會有種覺得個層搭lift既係阻撚住哂<br />\n係阻撚住哂 大佬 唔係你按停我到左地下出左lift啦一早你住1 2 3 樓你都要花幾分鐘來按lift都唔用分零鐘時間行落樓你冇撚野呀<br />\n咁你講1 2 樓管理費平啲呢個問題其實大家都明你意思既 大家交既費用基本上一樣大家都可以享用住宅既公共設施既<br />\n所以講真其實我覺得唔需要話 1 2 3 樓啲住客既<br />\n係只不過有時你望住部lift差唔多到地下個時停係1 2 3 樓你會有時有種莫名既憤怒姐"},{"pid":"b4e0f289c3b3ab2e511f2468e950b77145095a92","tid":223421,"uid":47700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T13:18:08.000Z","msg":"唔係返工返學時段都ok嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但繁忙時段唔知點解啲住123樓嘅廢老好鍾意係呢啲時間搭lift<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b292df742e085203c86a9d63d2e2c61a8c6b26c","tid":223421,"uid":89064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T19:07:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係返工返學時段都ok嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但繁忙時段唔知點解啲住123樓嘅廢老好鍾意係呢啲時間搭lift<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最仆街就係同一間屋既人入左LIFT, 跟住禁實部LIFT等另一個人關好鐵閘入LIFT先關門, 仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"705a74429e3d3bec1b90d7b24425105c48e371fe","tid":223421,"uid":48633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T19:11:54.000Z","msg":"住6樓都廢事等，落樓行樓梯算。上樓另計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利伸 以前住唐樓7樓"},{"pid":"648657a30c947777593ded2a2a35bdc142c8d260","tid":223421,"uid":26084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T19:35:18.000Z","msg":"如果拎重嘢咪搭囉"},{"pid":"a75d4f01766ee11094c57f559ad342d10a0f6fcf","tid":223421,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2