>\n係只不過有時你望住部lift差唔多到地下個時停係1 2 3 樓你會有時有種莫名既憤怒姐</blockquote><br />\n有咩好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我住2x樓但從來唔覺1 2 3樓嘅人入lift有咩問題 老老實實2x樓落黎其實好多層入lift都會阻到我 但無咩嘢喎<br />\n你自己脾氣暴躁炸掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a00ce8755f68c7ad5f53eb6021e853788900d5c8","tid":223421,"uid":33004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T06:57:57.000Z","msg":"覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返工返學時間覺得好撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚心行落去啦屌<br />\n利申住新樓 total 60幾層高速lift <br />\n如果層層停會搞到好撚慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}